      <title>彭博法国民调：极右翼勒庞领先优势扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/bloomberg-french-poll-of-polls-far-right-le-pen-s-lead-widens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的民意调查显示，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的极右翼国民联盟在周日法国提前立法选举第一轮投票前扩大了领先优势，而其竞争对手则势头减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/bloomberg-french-poll-of-polls-far-right-le-pen-s-lead-widens</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克里姆林宫助手称印度总理莫迪将访问俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/indian-premier-modi-to-visit-russia-kremlin-aide-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克里姆林宫外交政策助理尤里·乌沙科夫称，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪预计将自乌克兰战争爆发以来首次访问俄罗斯，具体日期将稍后公布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/indian-premier-modi-to-visit-russia-kremlin-aide-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 07:30:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯称应重新考虑对朝鲜的制裁--塔斯社</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/russia-says-north-korea-sanctions-should-be-reconsidered-tass</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统普京的助手表示，国际社会现在应该重新考虑联合国对朝鲜制裁制度需要做哪些改变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/russia-says-north-korea-sanctions-should-be-reconsidered-tass</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:48:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>《金融时报》称中国企业与马来西亚官员会面讨论美国关税问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/chinese-firms-meet-malaysian-officials-on-us-tariffs-ft-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《金融时报》报道，中国企业高管一直在马来西亚会见政府高层官员，寻求保证如果将制造业转移到马来西亚，可以避免美国关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/chinese-firms-meet-malaysian-officials-on-us-tariffs-ft-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦将在打击武装分子前建立“共识”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/pakistan-to-build-consensus-before-operation-against-militants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦国防部长表示，巴基斯坦政府正努力在对武装分子发动新军事行动之前建立全国范围的“共识”。此前，中国对其在巴基斯坦的项目遭到袭击表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/pakistan-to-build-consensus-before-operation-against-militants</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:35:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸军政府首脑为高级僧侣遇害事件罕见道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/myanmar-junta-chief-makes-rare-apology-for-senior-monk-s-killing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸军政府领导人敏昂莱在上周一座著名佛教寺院的住持被安全部队杀害后，罕见地向该寺院道歉，这一事态发展可能引发传统上支持军方的僧侣的大规模抗议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/myanmar-junta-chief-makes-rare-apology-for-senior-monk-s-killing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:11:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚警察在税收表决前封锁议会大楼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-police-barricade-parliament-precinct-before-vote-on-taxes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚立法者准备就引发广泛抗议的新税法进行投票，警方在议会周围设置了路障，企业关闭了首都的办公场所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/kenyan-police-barricade-parliament-precinct-before-vote-on-taxes</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 06:08:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国海域冲突如何导致菲律宾船员失去手指</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/how-china-sea-clash-caused-philippine-sailor-to-lose-his-finger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名菲律宾水手周二首次详细描述了他在 6 月 17 日北京和马尼拉船只在南海冲突中失去拇指的经历。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-25/how-china-sea-clash-caused-philippine-sailor-to-lose-his-finger</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 05:24:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞指责马克龙散布“内战”言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/macron-says-extreme-opposition-parties-would-lead-to-civil-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞表示，法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙指责极右翼国民联盟和左翼联盟的议程可能导致“内战”，这表明他知道自己将输掉于周日开始的立法投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/macron-says-extreme-opposition-parties-would-lead-to-civil-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 18:14:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非各政党接近就内阁职位达成一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/south-african-political-parties-nearing-accord-on-cabinet-posts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，南非两个最大政党即将就各自部长人数达成一致，以便与其他小党派组建广泛的联合政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-24/south-african-political-parties-nearing-accord-on-cabinet-posts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2024 15:16:47 GMT</pubDate>
